            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab><persName><name ref="Ragibertus">Rachipert</name></persName> filio
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Radaldus">Raduald</name></persName> de
                            <placeName ref="#places/555"
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Cereals #Fruits/vegetables #Hay/fodder"
                            >Interaccule</placeName>
                        <foreign>dona a</foreign> Deo et tibi <rs key="#Churches">eclesie</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/307">beatissimi Sancti
                            Angeli,</orgName> qui est prope <rs key="#Walls">muro</rs>
                        <rs key="#Cities">civitatis</rs> ista <placeName key="#Cities #Walls"
                            >Lucense</placeName>, ubi nunc <persName key="#Other_clerics"><name
                                ref="Deusdona">Deusdona</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_clerics">clericus</rs> presol esse videtur, omnia in omnibus
                        rebus meis quanta nunc presenti die avire videor; id est <rs
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">casa</rs> avitationis me cum curte, <rs
                            key="#Fruits/vegetables">orto</rs>, <rs key="#Cereals">terris</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Hay/fodder">pratis, pascuis</rs>, cultum vel incultum, movile vel
                        inmobile seo semovenitbus. <foreign>Ne riserva il diritto di uso
                            vitalizio</foreign> a genetrice mea <persName><name ref="Auderada"
                                >Auderada</name></persName>. (â€¦) Quem vero pagina, sicut superius
                        legitur, detantem Alpert et <persName key="#Writer"><name ref="Prandulus"
                                >Prandulo</name></persName> iscrivere rogavi. Actum <placeName
                            ref="#places/4">Luca</placeName>. <foreign>Sottoscrizioni</foreign>: +
                        Rachipert; + <persName key="#Witness #Vir_devotus/vir_honestus"><name
                                ref="Paulicius">Paulici</name></persName> filio quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Cliffo">Cliffi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Vir_devotus/vir_honestus">viri devoti</rs> testis; + <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Cunimundus">Cunimundi</name></persName>
                        germano eius testis; + <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Cillulus"
                                >Cilluli</name></persName> filio quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Albinus">Albini</name></persName> testis; <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Albertus">Alpert</name></persName> (ss).
                            <foreign>Scrive</foreign>: Prandulo.</ab>
                        </div>
                    </div>
